{{Underlinked|date=October 2017}}

The '''Crested Butte Wild Flower Festival''' is a week-long event that takes place annually in July in [[Crested Butte, Colorado]], USA.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.allcrestedbutte.com/events/wildflower_festival.php |title=Wildflower Festival |work=allcrestedbutte.com |accessdate=6 June 2013}}</ref> The flower-focused festival includes hikes, tours, workshops and performances, and raises awareness of [[environmental issues]], including the importance of preserving [[wild flowers]] in the city. Thousands of artists, vendors and people from all over the world gather in the town of [[Crested Butte]] for a weekend of art, food, dancing and music.

